job = []
salary = []
practice_time = []
describe = []
educational = []
release_time = []
headcount = []
company = []
size = []
address = []
trade = []


for i in range(1, 51):
    url ='https://www.ciwei.net/internship/search/sc1-pg{}'.format(i)
    print('正在第{}个一级页面'.format(i))
    headers = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/95.0.4638.69 Safari/537.36'}
    web = requests.get(url, headers=headers)        # 发送访问请求
    dom = etree.HTML(web.text)     # 对网页源码进行解析
    job1 = dom.xpath('//*[@class="job-title___1tyad"]/@title')           # 岗位名称
    salary1 = dom.xpath('//*[@class="job-salary___3cvWI"]/text()')    # 薪资待遇
    practice_time1 = dom.xpath('//*[@class="job-address-edu___dT8Tv"]/span[3]/text()')   # 实习时长
    href1 = dom.xpath('//*[@class="ant-col ant-col-14"]//a/@href')
    href2 = dom.xpath('//*[@class="name-authentication___3NNOB"]/a/@href')
    
    describe1 = []
    educational1 = []
    release_time1 = []
    headcount1 = []
    for j in href1:
        url_sub1 = 'https://www.ciwei.net{}'.format(j)    # 二级页面的网址
        print('...正在爬取【岗位详情】二级网页：{}'.format(url_sub1))
        web_sub1 = requests.get(url_sub1, headers=headers)
        dom_sub1 = etree.HTML(web_sub1.text)
        describe2 = dom_sub1.xpath('//ul[@class="job-desc___3DHRK"]//span/text()')[0]  # 获取工作描述
        educational2 = dom_sub1.xpath('//span[@class="job-address-edu___3rBR9"]/text()[2]')[0]  # 学历要求
        headcount2 = dom_sub1.xpath('//span[@class="job-address-edu___3rBR9"]/text()[3]')[0]  # 招聘人数
        release_time2 = dom_sub1.xpath('//p[@class="time___1pbLo"]/text()[1]')[0] # 发布时间
        describe1.append(describe2)
        educational.append(educational2)
        headcount1.append(headcount2)
        release_time1.append(release_time2)
        time.sleep(1)
    
    company1 = []
    size1 = []
    address1 = []
    trade1 = []
    for k in href2:
        url_sub2 = 'https://www.ciwei.net{}'.format(k)    # 二级页面的网址
        print('...正在爬取【公司详情】二级网页：{}'.format(url_sub2))
        web_sub2 = requests.get(url_sub2, headers=headers)
        dom_sub2 = etree.HTML(web_sub2.text)
        #尝试提取，失败则取空
        try:
            company2 =dom_sub2.xpath('//h1/text()')[0]   # 公司名称
        except:
            company2 = None
        try:
            address2 = dom_sub2.xpath('//div[@class="txt___1RUWi"]/text()[2]')[0]           # 公司地址
        except:
            address2 = None
        try:
            trade2 = dom_sub2.xpath('//span[@class="strong___19nzO"][1]/text()[2]')[0]           # 企业领域
        except:
            trade2 = None
        try:
            size2 =dom_sub2.xpath('//span[@class="strong___19nzO"][2]/text()[2]')[0]    # 公司规模
        except:
            size2 = None
        company1.append(company2)
        size1.append(size2)
        address1.append(address2)
        trade1.append(trade2)
        time.sleep(1)
        
    # 对获取到的中间结果进行存储

    job.extend(job1)
    salary.extend(salary1)
    practice_time.extend(practice_time1)
    describe.extend(describe1)
    educational.extend(educational1)
    headcount.extend(headcount1)
    release_time.extend(release_time1)
    company.extend(company1)
    size.extend(size1)
    address.extend(address1)
    trade.extend(trade1)
    
    time.sleep(1)

job_information = job_information.loc[job_information['薪资待遇']!='面议'].reset_index(drop=True)
# 将薪资单位转化为“元/天”，并求区间的均值
for i in range(job_information.shape[0]):
    salary = job_information['薪资待遇'][i]
    ls = re.findall('\d+',salary)
    ls_sum = int(ls[0])+int(ls[1])
    if salary[-3:] == 'K/月':
        job_information['薪资待遇'][i] = round(ls_sum*1000/30/2,2)
    else:
        job_information['薪资待遇'][i] = round(ls_sum/2,2)
job_information['薪资待遇'] = job_information['薪资待遇'].astype(float)

# 分词、去停用词
# job_information['工作描述'] = job_information['工作描述'].apply(jieba.lcut)

# 检查'工作描述'列中的元素是否都是字符串
if not job_information['工作描述'].apply(lambda x: isinstance(x, str)).all():
    # 如果不是，将非字符串元素转换为字符串
    job_information['工作描述'] = job_information['工作描述'].apply(str)

# 现在可以安全地应用jieba.lcut
job_information['工作描述'] = job_information['工作描述'].apply(jieba.lcut)

# 分词、去停用词
with open('../数据/stoplist.txt', encoding='utf-8',mode='r') as f:
    stopWords = [i.strip() for i in f.readlines()] # 以列表的形式读取
stopWords += ['•']

job_information['工作描述'] = job_information['工作描述'].apply(lambda x:[i for i in x if i not in stopWords] )
